tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE FilamentInventory (
 filament_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 filament_name VARCHAR(255),
 filament_type VARCHAR(50),
 filament_quantity INT,
 filament_price DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE Filaments (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  color VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  material VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  diameter DECIMAL(4,2) NOT NULL,
  price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Parts (
  part_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  part_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  manufacturer VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  quantity INT NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE filaments (
  filament_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  filament_name VARCHAR(255),
  filament_type VARCHAR(100),
  filament_color VARCHAR(50),

);

CREATE TABLE parts (
  part_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  part_name VARCHAR(255),
  part_category VARCHAR(100),

  part_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  part_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
  inventory_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

);

CREATE TABLE filaments (
    filament_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    filament_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    filament_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    filament_color VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    filament_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE parts (
    part_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    part_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    part_material VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    part_color VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    part_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    inventory_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_id INT NOT NULL,
    item_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_id INT NOT NULL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    transaction_date DATE NOT NULL,
    quantity_changed INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Filaments (
  filament_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  filament_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  filament_color TEXT,
  filament_material TEXT NOT NULL,
  filament_diameter DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Parts (
  part_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  part_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  part_description TEXT,
  part_material TEXT NOT NULL,
  part_weight DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Orders (
  order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_id INTEGER REFERENCES Suppliers(supplier_id),
  product_id INTEGER REFERENCES Parts(part_id),
  order_quantity INTEGER NOT NULL,
  order_date DATE
);
